      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "AMAZING MOLLY (1) has never missed the money at this C&D. Jumps from the inside draw. Latest effort finished 3rd over 340m at this track beaten 2.5 lengths (20.35) behind Orana Jim in a Maiden on February 9. Rates on top and should go close. KIANDO PIPER (4) did a good job to finish second last time out over 340m at this track (20.31) in a Maiden, the second top-three finish on the trot. Rates a winning chance on best. BLOCKER'S MATE (8) has missed the frame at his last two but did run well three back when second (20.44) in a Maiden at this track. Well placed here and can atone this time. TRUST A PROCESS (6) is usually competitive but a maiden win eludes.",
